- `/generate-tests` -- create unit, integration, and E2E test suites
- `/api-docs` -- generate OpenAPI 3.1.0 documentation
- `/refactor-legacy` -- systematic code refactoring with SOLID principles
- `/architecture-review` -- C4 diagrams and dependency analysis
- `/migration` -- safe database migration generation
