## Dashboard

The dashboard provides a visual overview of project health, SBOM, security vulnerabilities, and license compliance.

### How to Open

- **Windows:** Run `.windsurf/tools/dashboard.bat`
- **macOS/Linux:** Run `.windsurf/tools/dashboard.sh`
- **Manual / Devin:** Start the config server (`node .windsurf/tools/config-server.js`), then access `http://localhost:3847/dashboard`
- **API only (Devin):** `curl http://localhost:3847/dashboard-data` for JSON data without browser

### Dashboard Endpoints

| Endpoint               | Method | Description                                           |
| ---------------------- | ------ | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| `/dashboard`           | GET    | Serve dashboard HTML                                  |
| `/dashboard-data`      | GET    | Read aggregated dashboard state                       |
| `/dashboard-data`      | POST   | Append a workflow run entry                           |
| `/generate-sbom`       | GET    | Generate SBOM JSON from project dependencies          |
| `/security-scan`       | GET    | Run npm audit and generate security report            |
| `/license-check`       | GET    | Evaluate SBOM against license policy                  |
| `/dashboard-aggregate` | GET    | Aggregate all data into dashboard-data.json           |
| `/dashboard-full-scan` | GET    | Run SBOM + Security + License + Aggregate in sequence |
| `/sbom-data`           | GET    | Read SBOM JSON for current project                    |
| `/security-data`       | GET    | Read security scan results                            |
| `/license-data`        | GET    | Read license evaluation results                       |
| `/architecture-data`   | GET    | Read architecture diagrams and last review run        |
| `/merge-agents-md`     | GET/POST | Smart merge ASP sections into existing AGENTS.md   |
| `/agents-md-status`    | GET    | Check AGENTS.md existence and merge state             |
| `/update-agents-md-rules` | GET | Sync Active Rules section with actual rule files      |

### Data Storage

All dashboard data is stored under `.windsurf/` in the target project:

- `.windsurf/dashboard-data.json` -- aggregated state
- `.windsurf/dashboard/sbom/` -- SBOM per project
- `.windsurf/dashboard/security/` -- security scan results
- `.windsurf/dashboard/licenses/` -- license evaluations
- `.windsurf/dashboard/runs/[workflow]/[YYYY-MM-DD]/[timestamp]/` -- per-run reports (findings.json + report.md), grouped by date for git-friendly team collaboration
- `.windsurf/backups/` -- AGENTS.md backups created before merge operations
- `.windsurf/docs/` -- generated documentation (ARCHITECTURE.md, BOM.md, API.md, diagrams/)

### Workflow Integration

All 12 workflows include a final "Save to Dashboard" step that persists run results to `dashboard-data.json` and writes detailed reports to `.windsurf/dashboard/runs/`.
<!-- ASP:dashboard:END -->

<!-- ASP:repository-structure:BEGIN -->
## Repository Structure

```
project-root/
  AGENTS.md                          # Auto-generated/merged by installer (do not copy manually)
  .windsurf/                         # Source of truth for rules, workflows, tools
    rules/                           # Behavioral rules (read by all agents)
    workflows/                       # Workflow definitions (Windsurf: native, others: read & execute)
    tools/                           # Config server, dashboard, installer, MCP workflow server
    templates/                       # AGENTS.md template for merge operations
    backups/                         # AGENTS.md backups before merge
    dashboard/                       # Dashboard data (JSON)
    docs/                            # Generated documentation
  .devin/                            # Devin adapter layer
    skills/                          # Devin Skills (wrappers to .windsurf/workflows/)
      ...
    config.json                      # MCP server registration
```
<!-- ASP:repository-structure:END -->
